Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <channel-interface> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT channel-interface (comment*, extends*, parameters?)>
 <!ATTLIST channel-interface
      name                NMTOKEN   #REQUIRED>

virtual const char* ChannelInterfaceElement::getAttributeDefault ( int  k  )  const [virtual]

It should return NULL if k is out of range (i.e. negative or greater than getNumAttributes()), or if the attribute is #REQUIRED; and return "" if the attribute is #IMPLIED.
